tables.table_schema: Analyzing delivery routes and optimizing transportation efficiency

CREATE TABLE delivery_schedule (
    schedule_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    route_id INT,
    vehicle_id INT,
    delivery_time TIMESTAMP,
    CONSTRAINT fk_route FOREIGN KEY (route_id) REFERENCES delivery_routes(route_id),
    CONSTRAINT fk_vehicle FOREIGN KEY (vehicle_id) REFERENCES delivery_vehicles(vehicle_id)
);
